<p>
<note n="0318001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0318001">Abhisāma（勝金色）。</note>
<note n="0319001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0319001">讀為 ekanavute（異本）。</note>
<note n="0319002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0319002">Anantajāli（無限焰）。</note>
<note n="0320001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0320001">Amitañjala（無量水）。</note>
<note n="0320001-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0320001-1">Jutindhara（持輝）。</note>
<note n="0321001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0321001">讀為 pādap' uttme（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0321002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0321002">Sūriyassama（太陽似）。</note>
<note n="0322001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0322001">Candupama（月似）。</note>
<note n="0323001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0323001">在暹羅本中加入左之一偈：吾取佛之鉢，施毘耶拉花，更以清淨心，奉與達道佛。</note>
